_list0 = open('data.json').read().split("\n")
print(_list0)
print("\n")
names = []
prices = []

for i in range(1, len(_list0) - 1):
    names.append(_list0[i].split(':')[0].strip('" "'))
    prices.append(float(_list0[i].split(':')[1].strip(',').strip('" "')))
max_price = prices[0]
for i in prices:
    if max_price < i:
        max_price = i
print(names)
print()
print(prices)
print("max_price ", max_price)
